&gt;<br>
&gt;While there are considerable engineering difficulties with<br>
OF2/B2H6, they are simply a matter of degree, not a matter<br>
of complexity. Complexity kills, I firmly believe.<br>
&gt;<br>
I would much rather address issues... of degree as long as it<br>
keeps the complexity of the design down.<br>
&gt;<br>
&gt; Tri-propellant involves extra piping and more importantly<br>
valves, and even more importantly pumps. Can a CH4 pump<br>
